<h2 id="Properties">Properties</h2>

<p><em>Inherits properties from its parent, {{domxref("HTMLElement")}}.</em></p>

<dl>
 <dt>{{domxref("HTMLFontElement.color")}}</dt>
 <dd>Is a {{domxref("DOMString")}} that reflects the {{htmlattrxref("color", "font")}} HTML attribute, containing either a named color or a color specified in the hexadecimal #RRGGBB format.</dd>
 <dt>{{domxref("HTMLFontElement.face")}}</dt>
 <dd>Is a {{domxref("DOMString")}} that reflects the {{htmlattrxref("face", "font")}} HTML attribute, containing a comma-separated list of one or more font names.</dd>
 <dt>{{domxref("HTMLFontElement.size")}}</dt>
 <dd>Is a {{domxref("DOMString")}} that reflects the {{htmlattrxref("size", "font")}} HTML attribute, containing either a font size number ranging from 1 to 7 or a relative size to the {{htmlattrxref("size", "basefont")}} attribute of the {{HTMLElement("basefont")}} element, for example -2 or +1.</dd>
</dl>

